<li>Wright, James K. 2007. <i>Schoenberg, Wittgenstein, and the Vienna Circle.</i> Bern: Verlag Peter Lang. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-3-03911-287-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-3-03911-287-6">978-3-03911-287-6</a></li>
<li>Wright, James K. and Alan M. Gillmor (eds.). 2009. <i>Schoenberg's Chamber Music, Schoenberg's World.</i> New York: Pendragon Press. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-57647-130-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-57647-130-2">978-1-57647-130-2</a></li></ul>
</div>
